    public abstract class EnergyScreen<T extends EnergyScreenHandler>
extends net.minecraft.client.gui.screen.ingame.HandledScreen<T>
    Energy Screen is a simple class that adds a meter for energy and configuration panel to draw the panel (type dependent on panel mode specified in the energy class) on a sidebar to configure the machine's input/output.
